      * Tests OCCURS DEPENDING ON. Expected: FIRST then SECND
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. TYPE-OCCURS-DEPENDING-TEST.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-CNT  PIC 9(2) VALUE 2.
       01 WS-TBL.
          05 WS-ITEM PIC X(5) OCCURS 1 TO 5 TIMES DEPENDING ON WS-CNT.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PARA.
           MOVE "FIRST" TO WS-ITEM(1).
           MOVE "SECND" TO WS-ITEM(2).
           DISPLAY WS-ITEM(1).
           DISPLAY WS-ITEM(2).
           STOP RUN.
